title: Poker Superstars III
description: Are you ready for the next Challenge?! Poker Superstars III Gold Chip Challenge raises the stakes with new superstars, new gold chips to win for great plays and a brand new challenge play mode. Of course, there&#039;s always the dynamic and competitive tournament mode, just like the TV show, or you can sit in for a cash game! Two different levels of challenge let you tune the game to the play level you want. The Superstars are up for the new challenge, are you?
